snippet.title: Chuck's Challenge 3D 2020 - Launch Trailer - PC, Mac & Linux - Steam
snippet.description: Here's the Launch Trailer for Chuck's Challenge 3D 2020, the spiritual successor to Chip's Challenge. We've been working over the last 14 months to create a new remastered version with enhanced gameplay and graphics. Available on Steam - http://store.steampowered.com/app/262590
